word_mean_info__list.difference: 普通用词。或指持续而不停止，或有一段中断后又继续下去。
通俗用词，多用于口语中。go on+-ing表暂停后继续做原事，即后继续的内容与原来的内容相同。go on+不定式指做完某事后，接着做不同的另一件事。
表示成功，强调完成某件想往或企图去做的事，与fail相对。
指持续不断地成功，也指越来越成功。
指蓬勃发展，常指显而易见的成功。
指处于成功、繁荣、进步的顶盛阶段。

bilingual.target: 她告诉我，“努力工作才能成功。”

bilingual.source: If you succeed in doing something, you manage to do it.
bilingual.target: 如果你成功做某事，你就完成了它。

bilingual.source: They always talk about what will happen if I don't succeed.
bilingual.target: 他们总是谈论如果我不成功会怎样。

bilingual.source: Some young people are very determined to succeed at a sport.
bilingual.target: 一些年轻人非常坚定要在运动中取得成功。

bilingual.source: Schools have to find ways to help their students succeed while keeping spending down.
bilingual.target: 学校必须找到在减少开支的同时帮助学生成功的方法。
我真诚地希望你能成功。

list.abstract: succeed（英[səkˈsiːd]，美[səkˈsiːd]），英语单词，动词，译为成功；接替；继承。短语搭配有succeed in doing（成功做某事）、succeed to（继承）。例句为“Unless you work hard, you will not succeed.（除非你努力工作，否则你不会成功。）” succeed的名词是success，形容词是successive、successful、succeeding，过去分词为succeeded。

yingyinNormal.en: So the simple truth is, when women succeed, America succeeds.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，简单的事实就是，妇女成功了，美国就成功了。

yingyinNormal.en: Then let's succeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们成功就好了。

yingyinNormal.en: What if we put Milkin in a position to succeed. Now, I don't care if Milkin actually succeeds.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我们让米尔金有机会取得成功呢？我并不在乎米尔金是不是真能成功。

yingyinNormal.en: I like to back people who want to succeed. Take yourself as an example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我愿意支持渴望成功的人，你自己就是个例子。

yingyinNormal.en: He's smart, he's a marketing genius and he'll do whatever it takes to succeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他聪明，他是市场营销天才，他知道怎么才能走向成功

yingyinNormal.en: I only succeed with you guys if I get my teaching across as effectively as he did.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我像他一样有效地对你们进行教学，才算是成功了。

yingyinNormal.en: When our veterans have the opportunity to succeed, our whole nation is stronger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我们的退伍军人拥有了成功的机会，我们整个国家会变得更加强大。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I don't know, I mean, let's say we succeed in proving that our consciousness creates reality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我说不好，就算我们成功证明了我们的意识创造现实。

yingyinNormal.en: To succeed, we must embrace all our realities, especially the harsh realities that we wish weren't true.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要成功就得拥抱所有的现实，特别是难以接受的严酷现实。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I reckon you work hard and you deserve to succeed. You just have to stick at it and you will.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我倒觉得，你很努力，应该获得成功只要你继续坚持，你不能放弃。

yingyinNormal.en: And in 1984, I launched my own television show with a relentless determination to succeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在1984年，我推出了自己的电视栏目，而这靠的是自己追求成功的坚定决心。

yingyinNormal.en: I have no doubt you will succeed in that as well. But you will do so without the support you are about to ask of me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你最后会成功，我深信不疑，即使不向我寻求帮助，你也能如愿。

yingyinNormal.en: If we succeed, let it be for all of Panem and let it be forever. Yes, you already made history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我们成功了，施惠国会永获自由，我们的起义也会永垂不朽，是的，你们已经创造了历史。

yingyinNormal.en: You can listen to this naysayer, but I promise you this; if we succeed all will share in the wealth of the mountain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们可以听他劝阻，不过，我保证如果成功，孤山的财富大家可以一起分享。

yingyinNormal.en: Kevin, I've known you your whole life. Well, except for those two minutes at the beginning. You've succeed at everything you've ever tried.
yingyinNormal.zh: 凯文，我都认识你一辈子了，除了最初的两分钟。你努力的每件事都成功了。

yingyinNormal.en: And I succeed. I perform my first surprise, illegal high wire walk. This is also the first time I get the taste of this sensation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 结果成功了，我进行了第一次出人意料的非法高空走钢索，我也第一次尝到那种兴奋的滋味。

yingyinNormal.en: Francis, I could be impeached if I do that. No, no. Look, Davis and Usher, they're in a position to protect you. They want you to succeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 弗兰西斯，如果我这么做会被弹劾。不会的，戴维斯和厄舍，他们可以保护你。他们希望你成功。

yingyinNormal.en: At the same time, it didn't stop me from aggressively going after the things I wanted. To succeed, I needed to see more than I alone could see. But standing in my way of doing that were the two biggest barriers everyone faces. Our ego and blind spot barriers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时它也没有阻止我奋发追寻想要的东西。我得看到比一己之力更多的东西才能成功。但我成功路上的障碍也是每个人面对的两个最大障碍，即自负和盲点。

yingyinNormal.en: When the city became a republic in 1965, few thought a country with so few resources and of vastly different ethnic groups could succeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新加坡于 1965 年宣布独立，当时有些人认为这个国家缺乏天然资源，又融合太多民族，难以获得成功。

yingyinNormal.en: But succeed it has, on an unimaginable scale!
yingyinNormal.zh: 但事实证明，新加坡获得了空前的成就！
